.TH start-cli-backup-policy-preview-change 1  "preview-change " 
.SH NAME
start\-cli\-backup\-policy\-preview\-change \- Preview an automatic backup retention policy change
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBstart\-cli backup policy preview\-change\fR [\fB\-\-keep\-rule\fR] [\fB\-\-latest\-only\fR] [\fB\-\-format\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fITARGET_ID\fR> <\fIPACKAGE_ID\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Preview an automatic backup retention policy change
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-keep\-rule\fR \fI<INTERVAL:COVERAGE>\fR
Version\-history rule INTERVAL:COVERAGE; accepts s, m, h, d, or w and may repeat
.TP
\fB\-\-latest\-only\fR
Keep only the latest automatic checkpoint
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR

.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fITARGET_ID\fR>
Backup target identifier
.TP
<\fIPACKAGE_ID\fR>
Package identifier
